folder: Dewey Avenue & Throggs Neck Boulevard, Bronx, NY
original_title: Bronx: Dewey Avenue - Throggs Neck Boulevard
text:
(1) Dewey Ave., at Throggs Neck Boulevard (vantage point). The view is eastward across Weir Creek and shows the Edgewater Park bungalow colony on the shore of Long Island Sound.

P. L. Sperr.

(2) A closer view of the same showing the Creek (right) and Sound more prominently.

July 1, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.
